query:
INSERT INTO users (email, name, role, partnerId, loginMethod, emailVerified, lastSignedIn, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT 'contato@somosamarna.com.br', contactName, 'parceiro', id, 'oauth', 1, NOW(), NOW(), NOW() 
FROM partners 
WHERE contactEmail = 'contato@somosamarna.com.br' 
LIMIT 1;
